text:
Urbana, Illinois
December 12, 1952
Mr, James S, Miles
Executive Director
H.A.E.B,
119 Gregory Hall
Dear Jim:
Herewith check In amount of $1200 to cover
NAEB expenditures in behalf of the NAEB-FAE
Orants-in-Ald for 1952 Project,
Incidentally, this completes payment of all
grants and all expenditures. The entire
$80,000 has now been expended.
Frank E. Sohooley
Treasurer
FE8:es
cc: Oraydon Ausmus
